begin{aligned}
\text{Banyak apel perminggu} &= 1 \text{ apel per hari} \times 7 \text{ hari permingu} \\
&= 7 \text{ apel permingu}
\end{aligned}

\begin{aligned}
\text{Banyak apel per 3minggu} &= 7 \text{ apel perminggu} \times 3 \text{minggu} \\
&= 21 \text{ apel}
\end{aligned}

因此, Addison perlu beli \(\boxed{21}\) apel.

